ys used to finish together like you know, but - sometimes it might happen as - one had got something to do and then he wanted to get it done before - he went to school, so it'd ease him when he came - when he came home from - at - at teatime. That's way w
e used to work it. Well we had to do when us - we'd got to stop and work - you'd got to stop - when you were set a job you'd got to stop there while it were - you were finished. You couldn't go play.
