Well - he'd very seldom - that me dad used to sit down, only on a Sunday with us. 'Cos he were either on days and - afternoons you know. Afternoons, he never used to have 
his - he never used to have a dinner before he went to pit. On account of it all - you know, rifting - on him. With bend - with bending a lot.
