Oh no. It - you're all - if you sit - sit round and she'd start at front, agen the fire - nearly to the fire and come right away round. But sometimes she'd - she'd say well
 I'm going round this way this time. She'd turn round to the - if she served right she come to left, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 What if your dad was there, would he be served first?
