mes he'd - if you - want to do anything and he'd tell you once and he'd just come to you and say that - you - I've told you that once - that's not way to do it, and just give you a - a clink at earh}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10446766\charrsid2837000 ole}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 . Then - you think on then.
