\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Would you go to chapel together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 
Well - with - now then - we didn't used to go to chapel that day at Christmas Day. Now I think meself. 'Cos we were - all active at home, don't you see. Mm. All at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 You'd all stay there and you'd have Christmas lunch together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Yes, that were right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 And sing carols in the afternoon and then have tea and then sing carols in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Well when you'd had a damned good dinner and - a Christmas dinner and - you didn'
t feel as if you want to go anywhere did you. The same as now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Was there anybody in the house who used to play a musical instrument? Did you have piano or anything?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Me dad used to have a - I don't know what they call it, but he used to put it t
o his mouth and there used to be - be about three inches long and he used to - hit a thing at side on it. And he'd play - play it at - he could play it like the devil. Play anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 What about the rest of the family, was there anybody else in the family who could play an instrument?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 No, he was about the only one, well - we'd have a tin whistle or something like that and we'd - we couldn't play a note on, make a noise.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 You didn't have a piano?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Oh no. Anybody that had a piano in them days they were - millionaires. We thought they thought - we - well, we used to think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 But all the family used to sing together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Aye, we all used to sing together. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Were any of you in the church choir or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Well I - I used to be - in Primitive choir. Well we all was, all on us, we all on joined in that. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Were there any sort of musical activities in Brierley?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Did you have any village choirs or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Well we'd - we'd a glee party but - it - in Brierley. And - I never were in it thought, I wouldn't, 'cos I didn't like - I didn't like -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Did any of the rest of the family belong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 But - Ben, that were him as were next to me. He - he were in it and - well - they - it was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10446766\charrsid2837000 proper glee}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 
 party. It were what they call - Turners used to run it. And - they won - they won cup one year. I know - I've a medal somewhere in house now what our - what - what Ben won, and - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10446766\charrsid2837000 you\rquote 
re}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000  a bit hard up and - he said, well how much will they
 give me for this Frank? So - I said, I won't give you now for it 'cos it's no good to me. Well how much money do you want yet, so - he says - give me half a crown for it? And - I don't know how much they were valid at, but - I said what it - well - it we
re a grand, it were a nice medal what they got. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10446766\charrsid2837000 And - they won this here cup for a glee party did - did Brierley that year. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 
And it were - Turners that - run it, run this here glee party. There used to be - there used to be him and Gunner, used to always mat
e together, they were - they - well they broke away from church - they broke away from chapel and went to church, used to be in church choir. At Brierley.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 But Ben was the only one in the family who singing aspirations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Oh aye, aye. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Apart from Christmas did you used to sing together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Every Sunday night. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10446766\charrsid2837000 
Every Sunday night we always - that was only time we were allowed in.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 It was after you'd come back from the chapel, you would go into the front room and sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Well - we - we'd had us tea, it were nearly time for to go back to chapel, six o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Was it after you came home from chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 And - and then we'd have a sing for about half an hour. And then of course - upstairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Did your parents used to sing together, did they used to play games with the children in the house, can you remember playing cards?
