Oh - oh aye, you could - there were books here, you could pick 'em up and - and - what she used to say - if you've now to do just get that. And of course there used to school books, about - what you learned at school. Oh aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 You would get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10446766\charrsid2837000 prizes}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
