\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10446766\charrsid2837000 And I believe it's only prize as I have got.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2837000  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10446766\charrsid2837000 
