 books, where did the books come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10446766\charrsid2837000 
Well she used to buy - she used to buy books, there used to be stalls then - at Barnsley and me mother used to - if - she thought - she'd go and look at 'em and if she thought they were - they'd educate you, you know, she'd - bring you one. }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Of course then - you could get one of them for about sixpence.
