You would have to get changed in between. You say that on Saturdays this was more or less given up to playing games, were you allowed to play games on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 No, you wouldn't - no, no games
 on a Sunday. No. You'd got to - you might be sad in your room and - you might have orange to eat or something like that and - on a Sunday. You always -
