\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 In the house. Mm. Oh you were
n't allowed - you weren't allowed to go and - gallivanting off, into street and - causing trouble or out like that, you'd got to stop in. While it were chapel time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 You think your mum and dad thought it was wrong then to sort of play on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Oh they did, my word, aye. And me dad wouldn't do no work on a Sunday. No. He always used to say - Sunday were a rest day.
