No. They would - what? The - they're washing every day now with some on 'em. And if me mother see'd anybody with any - with any clothes out on a Sunday, by - she us to go nearly mad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Did your parents attend a place of worship or not, you said your mum went twice a day on Sundays, what about your dad, did he go to church?

