\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Mm. Mm. That's right.
