ee o'clock. Or a quarter past. And then they used - when - afternoon shift - afternoon shift they used to go down for two. Well they used to be - used to have to be off be - quarter to one, and he'd be coming home about half past ten at night, in them day
s. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7233525\charrsid2837000 But - no - seven hour - were no seven hours same as there is now for 'em. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 
There weren't. And in them days if - when they were miners at - if they didn't - if they didn't work they didn't get now.
