\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 No, only saving club that he used to have it were his - his - he used to have his - his - his own. And he was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Did they belong to any clubs for funerals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 No. And he - he used to keep his money - he used to keep his mother in - his money in a leather - in a leather bag, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7233525\charrsid2837000 fastened}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000  up with a piece of lace.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 He didn't belong to any clubs to cover him if he'd been off sick from work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Oh he was sick club in - at - at - pit like you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 He did belong to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 He were, he belonged to that one.
