\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 So she was your mother's sister-in-law in fact?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 So this was the usual pattern then, she would come in if your mother had another child?
