\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Yes - a lot of friends, well - 
you know - that - what we mean for friends, if they see that - you needed any help - such as - happen - they'd come and - do floor or out like that, well, me mother was - down the garden with me dad and - and us, they'd come and wash floor while - while -
 be - helping theirselves and - and Edith. Oh they were -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 So there was quite a lot of mutual visiting, your mum would go to their house and they would come to yours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Did this apply to your father's friends as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Well -
 he never - he never had time to make any friends, not proper. 'Cos as soon as he got home from work he were - you know - into the garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 So really it was sort of female friends of your mothers who used to be round about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Yes. Yes. That's right. He hadn't time to - he hadn't time to - he hadn't time to go - and have a drink at Three }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9966242\charrsid2837000 Horseshoes}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 . The only time when he used to have a drink when he used to go up to the Three }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9966242\charrsid2837000 Horseshoes}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000  were when he'd done a bit of business where he's selling pigs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 So your father shared your mother's friends rather than he had friends of his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Yes, that's right, he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Were friends invited into the house or did they just come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3486081 FP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 Oh they didn't let - come and - have a bit of a chat like you know
 but - not for long because he - he were - he were a fellow of this, what he - he liked to be - making - out that they were going like he'd make a bob or two. They had to do in them days, if - you'd to make it - same as I say well - make hay while sun shi
nes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 When these friends came would they be offered anything to eat or drink?
