- well, saying police woman, it were - Mr - it were policeman's wife. But - oh we'd some happy times. Everybody seemed to be right - I think they were more - more sociable than what they are now. Because there's some on 'em, they - they haven't time - the
y haven't time to look at you - they might say just - say good morning then off and - there we are.
