\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4270034 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12201098\charrsid2837000 So you wouldn't expect your }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9966242\charrsid2837000 parent\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
