No, they just - bit of company like you know - just your company and - pass time on. That's all they could - that's all they could do in them days.
 But - but I do - I do think that them days - I do think that the people seem - to be happier them days than what they are now. What with strikes and one thing and another we're having now well - I don't know. 'Cos the - everybody I think - everybody now 
