Well we went into the office and he persuaded us did the fellow - that cashier and I says - take it he says and - you might be able to better yourself he said whe
n you've been here about a fortnight. But - I think it were temper that did it you know. But any road, we pick - he - I didn't pick it up, I wouldn't have pick it up. He - sent some one of his staff to pick it up, it didn't take much picking up. I've six 
in but there were only seven and a tanner there.
