eve me not, we used to have to go down what they used to call workhouse down at Hemsworth. And - if you had a - well, there weren't so many that had owt in bank then. But they used to ask you that, have you got owt in bank. Well they knew damn well there 
w
as nowt. So - they says - well, when they'd asked all of them questions they used to ask you to - go - go outside, and - and then would shout you in. Well I'd just - I'd only just got door shut - at other side when he says, Mr Parkinson. I goes in. So he 
