e one said, well you won't - you won't have to pay rent. I said, and there's many more things all get missed and all but it's no use ten bob, I said, I'm not taking it. So I told him what to do with it. Any road, Mr Inglish that used to be at Grimethorpe,
 
he was a - a grand old gentleman - as I thought anyway - and he - he came galloping after me, he says come on Frank, he says, take this - take this he said, I'll see if I can get you some more but - there were nowt come. So he says sign - he says, sign th
at paper and - oh I said, I don't know whether I'm going to do or not but I thought well - a little bit's better than nowt. So any road I signed it for it but it never got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8128444\charrsid2837000 bigger}{\rtlch\fcs1 
